      <title>维珍航空退出中国市场，取消希思罗至上海航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/virgin-atlantic-pulls-out-of-china-axes-heathrow-shanghai-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维珍航空有限公司将从 10 月起暂停伦敦希思罗机场与上海之间的航班，放弃其飞往中国的唯一航线，因为避开俄罗斯领空的成本太高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/virgin-atlantic-pulls-out-of-china-axes-heathrow-shanghai-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
